{"tid":1367892,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"若果警察發癲暴亂，如何制止？","createTime":"2019-07-26T11:17:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T13:20:19.000Z","uid":290018,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"2879f7fe20133873f7954c02aede0d2a7354830f","tid":1367892,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:17:59.000Z","msg":"P牌仔，若果有冒犯，請勿見怪。<br />\n<br />\n睇到Barcode頭講完野，咁鬼多差佬跳出黎，就係度諗：政權中人有冇人係諗住推警察到邊緣，逼到佢地暴動？咁啱睇到區家麟篇文，講墨西哥1968年情況，好似我上述咁講：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%AA%B0%E9%96%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A7%8D-%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%97%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E6%87%B8%E6%A1%88/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25AA%25B0%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%2597%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2587%25B8%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&d=d2KrXihf468bG0awDawljkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=aa2a814f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E7%25A9%25B6%25E7%25AB%259F%25E8%25AA%25B0%25E9%2596%258B%25E7%259A%2584%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%25A7%258D-%25E4%25B8%2580%25E5%25AE%2597%25E4%25BB%258A%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%259F%25A5%25E9%2581%2593%25E7%259A%2584%25E5%25B1%25A0%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%2587%25B8%25E6%25A1%2588%2F&h=96310889\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/international/%E7%A9%B6%E7%AB%9F%E8%AA%B0%E9%96%8B%E7%9A%84%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E6%A7%8D-%E4%B8%80%E5%AE%97%E4%BB%8A%E5%A4%A9%E8%A6%81%E7%9F%A5%E9%81%93%E7%9A%84%E5%B1%A0%E6%AE%BA%E6%87%B8%E6%A1%88/</a><br />\n<br />\n警察暴亂，政府要求解放軍軍管，好似順利成章；小弟就諗，有冇機會避免（先利申，我都好想啲差佬冚包散；但送頭俾喪警，絕對唔值得）；短期有咩可以做？<br />\n<br />\n（1）727請各位克制，避兔同差佬衝突；<br />\n（2）請對警隊有影響力既人呼籲（曾蔭培，李明逵？）；<br />\n（3）文宣使外國向中共施壓？<br />\n（4）請聯合國關注，準備人道救援隊介入？（呢點有風險，可能會得罪中共面子）<br />\n<br />\n講出黎，想大家討論下。"},{"pid":"9ea9eba4f03fc258a69edf3ff2dc23c719d42742","tid":1367892,"uid":288351,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"1984香港警察暴動。自己研究下"},{"pid":"adfb7c0a531e9ff6b28a3ca577acd3b2bfa7ca7a","tid":1367892,"uid":134323,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:21:19.000Z","msg":"你個個差佬都同佢癲<br />\n<br />\n無斷正個班死都唔跟啦"},{"pid":"8ee45d954d01b6240a0c3a6a650e7d531dfa838d","tid":1367892,"uid":13663,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:22:31.000Z","msg":"冇糧出<br />\n完"},{"pid":"2de508d85d7c2afa1148c02b78003e1a2958adcd","tid":1367892,"uid":274658,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:23:08.000Z","msg":"老解進場<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36c1dfcda2ccacdbd1b0a6ac583569c62797e529","tid":1367892,"uid":46393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:24:57.000Z","msg":"係放老解唔該快啲 我同牛魔王等緊睇耶穌"},{"pid":"5e7c33cc315f414a13c41a221371bec8ed9c05e6","tid":1367892,"uid":32006,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:25:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 警犬cross over鄭乳驊"},{"pid":"22829e4215bb25df72a2de0ba2b50018af88778d","tid":1367892,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"襯佢地去食飯廁所果陣制止"},{"pid":"edd318deed848c37747249e5c7e2dab4da3fecda","tid":1367892,"uid":101328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T11:25:40.000Z","msg":"大家聽日一定要小心，唔好落單。班狗已經失曬控。連張建宗咁講一句都唔順氣。"},{"pid":"120d2f31992b5219dd2b3123d33f2deb1ea7c6cb","tid":1367892,"uid":180404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2879f7fe20133873f7954c02aede0d2a7354830f","tid":1367892,"uid":290018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":